#Repost @instagram

Professional footballer Paul Pogba (@paulpogba) is known for his ⚽ skills, but he recently discovered another talent... cooking.⁣⁣⁣
⁣
While at home with his family in France, he’s surprising his mom by making her one of his favorite childhood desserts. 🥮️ “I really hope my mom will love it,” says Paul. “But I hope she doesn’t eat everything because I love it too.” 😂⁣⁣
⁣
#TakeABreak with Paul (and his adorable son) as he dances and dribbles his way around the kitchen. 💯
